title: Sinn Féin budget alternative would boost opportunities for Irish Entrepreneurs - Tóibín (Sinn Féin)
text: ( Source : Sinn Féin ) 10 October , 2015 - by Peadar Tóibín TD Peadar Tóibín TD, Sinn Féin's spokesperson on Enterprise has outlined the manner in which Sinn Féin's pre-budget submission would suit the needs of Irish Entrepreneurs. Deputy
